des:
Six Word Stories are brief and powerful. Here are a collection of winter six word stories made for the snowy season, to cool you off, and add to the fun. Each story is randomly selected each time for your repeated listening enjoyment.

Have all of your friends play one, and see which one is the coolest. Happy winter!
